{"tid":2077823,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"《哭能左》木偶哥林師杰係TVB年薪有1.2m 屌打一眾連登仔","createTime":"2020-06-24T14:40:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-25T02:38:07.000Z","uid":240918,"like":8,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"e519f5b0f3b349dc74378262e000a6704ca4cee5","tid":2077823,"uid":240918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T14:40:47.000Z","msg":"林師傑曾傳受老婆歐陽巧瑩政見影響而遭無綫（TVB）冷待，他早前決定提早解約離開無綫。林師傑今日在社交網上載一張寫有「尊悲不分」的照片，表示跟無綫及星夢娛樂的合約正式結束。<br />\n<br />\n他說︰「多謝大家關心，今日終於正式結束同TVB+星夢嘅賓主關係！呢十一年黎（嚟）聽得咁多嘅一句說話『你幾時出歌呀？』呢句每次聽到，個心都那（揦）住那（揦）住痛。<br />\n<br />\n其實唔係唔想出，係冇得出。自己寫埋寫埋至少十幾廿首喺床（牀）下底，諗點樣蒙面出歌，諗左（咗）五年，做現實中嘅木偶哥。舊公司向我提出轉簽6 show合約，即意思一年保證有萬二蚊收入，雖然連一個月租金都不夠，但確實有如上天恩賜，我萬二分感激！<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ldy/20200624/s00009/f44bbf6fb836af6792f117efb87a49ac.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fldy%2F20200624%2Fs00009%2Ff44bbf6fb836af6792f117efb87a49ac.jpg&h=64283381&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我今年三十二，有家室，請問如何接受呢份恩賜呢？十一年前參加比賽立志做歌手，十一年後重新出發做獨立歌手，會遲嗎？要老婆陪我一齊捱窮，辛苦你了！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/4255828/org/b126838ffeadd5576acc0188c4b78d92.jpg/pIsmG0euR7YxI4v31DqDIsYiykaXgeWG1tbh8tbW4fI?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F4255828%2Forg%2Fb126838ffeadd5576acc0188c4b78d92.jpg%2FpIsmG0euR7YxI4v31DqDIsYiykaXgeWG1tbh8tbW4fI%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=8ea88b72&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n歐陽巧瑩之後亦於IG中出post，表示從來不希望跟無綫有關係的她，今日亦需要多謝無綫放生老公：「由我離開TVB至今，無論私下定公開，一句不是都冇講過，因為我真係唔想再同佢有關係。但今日我想講一句，多謝放生我老公。」不過她同時亦寸爆地叫無綫收回12,000元的恩賜：「請收返起你哋嘅恩賜，我哋會過得好好！」<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2345576/org/0d5df97880b73b068f6cacfde6268548.jpg/2lAYP8nu1HY1HmXCJv9ail-LrG2dsybLGR-PURkfj1E\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2345576%2Forg%2F0d5df97880b73b068f6cacfde6268548.jpg%2F2lAYP8nu1HY1HmXCJv9ail-LrG2dsybLGR-PURkfj1E&h=9c827f5f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n醬油：<a href=\"https://ol.mingpao.com/ldy/showbiz/latest/20200624/1592983488360/%E6%9E%97%E5%B8%AB%E5%82%91%E8%87%AA%E7%88%86%E9%9B%A2%E5%B7%A2%E5%8E%9F%E5%9B%A0-%E8%BD%89%E7%B0%BD1%E5%B9%B46%E9%A8%B7-%E6%AF%8F%E5%B9%B4%E8%90%AC%E4%BA%8C%E8%9A%8A%E6%94%B6%E5%85%A5%E9%9B%A3%E4%BB%A5%E7%B6%AD%E7%94%9F\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fol.mingpao.com%2Fldy%2Fshowbiz%2Flatest%2F20200624%2F1592983488360%2F%25E6%259E%2597%25E5%25B8%25AB%25E5%2582%2591%25E8%2587%25AA%25E7%2588%2586%25E9%259B%25A2%25E5%25B7%25A2%25E5%258E%259F%25E5%259B%25A0-%25E8%25BD%2589%25E7%25B0%25BD1%25E5%25B9%25B46%25E9%25A8%25B7-%25E6%25AF%258F%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E8%2590%25AC%25E4%25BA%258C%25E8%259A%258A%25E6%2594%25B6%25E5%2585%25A5%25E9%259B%25A3%25E4%25BB%25A5%25E7%25B6%25AD%25E7%2594%259F&d=Dkz3eIcuz1ZryPyeMF8ZPolFrThteLnMWGuqQSPs63E%3D&h=b9670177\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fol.mingpao.com%2Fldy%2Fshowbiz%2Flatest%2F20200624%2F1592983488360%2F%25E6%259E%2597%25E5%25B8%25AB%25E5%2582%2591%25E8%2587%25AA%25E7%2588%2586%25E9%259B%25A2%25E5%25B7%25A2%25E5%258E%259F%25E5%259B%25A0-%25E8%25BD%2589%25E7%25B0%25BD1%25E5%25B9%25B46%25E9%25A8%25B7-%25E6%25AF%258F%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E8%2590%25AC%25E4%25BA%258C%25E8%259A%258A%25E6%2594%25B6%25E5%2585%25A5%25E9%259B%25A3%25E4%25BB%25A5%25E7%25B6%25AD%25E7%2594%259F&h=f26935ac\" target=\"_blank\">https://ol.mingpao.com/ldy/showbiz/latest/20200624/1592983488360/%E6%9E%97%E5%B8%AB%E5%82%91%E8%87%AA%E7%88%86%E9%9B%A2%E5%B7%A2%E5%8E%9F%E5%9B%A0-%E8%BD%89%E7%B0%BD1%E5%B9%B46%E9%A8%B7-%E6%AF%8F%E5%B9%B4%E8%90%AC%E4%BA%8C%E8%9A%8A%E6%94%B6%E5%85%A5%E9%9B%A3%E4%BB%A5%E7%B6%AD%E7%94%9F</a><br />\n<br />\n支持蘋果日報LINK：<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200624/JQ3YTVGWNPTXGDLMSGCN5AU4WA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200624%2FJQ3YTVGWNPTXGDLMSGCN5AU4WA%2F&d=Dkz3eIcuz1ZryPyeMF8ZPolFrThteLnMWGuqQSPs63E%3D&h=783905ab\" 